comments: Class was Emergency Care On The Job (Or something close to that haha). Great teacher, made it very interesting. Did a great job!

Not an easy class, need to keep up on homework and workbook, but Deb\'s an excellent teacher with a lot of experience in the field. She uses many different teaching techniques and tools to help students learn, and is not tolerant of those that don\'t. I highly recommend her courses.
Class was fun and fairly easy
